{"prompt": "Develop an engaging platform for a local music school. The primary color should be a vibrant plum.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Harmony Haven Music School</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0e6f0;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #6A0DAD; /* Vibrant Plum */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #8a2be2; /* Lighter Plum */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #e0d8e6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #6A0DAD; /* Vibrant Plum */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        }\n        .section:last-child {\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n        .section h3 {\n            color: #8a2be2; /* Lighter Plum */\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n        }\n        .program-item, .instructor-item, .testimonial-item {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            border-left: 5px solid #6A0DAD; /* Vibrant Plum */\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .instructor-item img {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-right: 15px;\n            float: left;\n        }\n        .instructor-item::after {\n            content: \"\";\n            display: table;\n            clear: both;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .testimonial-item .author {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: right;\n            color: #6A0DAD; /* Vibrant Plum */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            background-color: #6A0DAD; /* Vibrant Plum */\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        #contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        #contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        #contact-form button {\n            background-color: #8a2be2; /* Lighter Plum */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #6A0DAD; /* Vibrant Plum */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Harmony Haven Music School</h1>\n        <p>Nurturing Musical Talent in Our Community</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#programs\">Programs</a>\n        <a href=\"#instructors\">Our Instructors</a>\n        <a href=\"#testimonials\">Testimonials</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Harmony Haven!</h2>\n            <p>At Harmony Haven Music School, we believe in the transformative power of music. We offer a vibrant and supportive environment for students of all ages and skill levels to explore their musical potential. Our passionate instructors are dedicated to providing high-quality music education, fostering creativity, and building a lifelong love for music.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"programs\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Programs</h2>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Private Lessons</h3>\n                <p>One-on-one instruction tailored to your individual learning style and musical goals. Available for piano, guitar, violin, voice, drums, and more!</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Group Classes</h3>\n                <p>Engaging group sessions for young learners, aspiring bands, and music theory enthusiasts. Perfect for social learning and collaborative music-making.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Ensembles & Bands</h3>\n                <p>Join our orchestras, choirs, and rock bands to experience the joy of playing music with others.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"program-item\">\n                <h3>Workshops & Masterclasses</h3>\n                <p>Specialized workshops led by renowned musicians to deepen your understanding and refine your skills.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"instructors\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Meet Our Talented Instructors</h2>\n            <div class=\"instructor-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/6A0DAD/ffffff?text=I1\" alt=\"Instructor 1\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Ms. Clara Barton</h3>\n                    <p><strong>Instrument:</strong> Piano</p>\n                    <p>With over 20 years of teaching experience, Ms. Barton is a patient and inspiring piano instructor.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"instructor-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/8a2be2/ffffff?text=I2\" alt=\"Instructor 2\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Mr. Leo Vance</h3>\n                    <p><strong>Instrument:</strong> Guitar</p>\n                    <p>A professional guitarist and energetic teacher, Mr. Vance brings passion and modern techniques to his lessons.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"instructor-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/80/6A0DAD/ffffff?text=I3\" alt=\"Instructor 3\">\n                <div>\n                    <h3>Ms. Anya Sharma</h3>\n                    <p><strong>Instrument:</strong> Voice</p>\n                    <p>Ms. Sharma, a classically trained vocalist, excels at helping students find their unique voice and build confidence.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"testimonials\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>What Our Students Say</h2>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"Harmony Haven has been a wonderful experience for my daughter. The instructors are amazing and she's learned so much!\"</p>\n                <p class=\"author\">- Sarah K.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"testimonial-item\">\n                <p>\"Finally found a music school that makes learning fun and accessible. Highly recommend!\"</p>\n                <p class=\"author\">- David L.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to start your musical journey? Fill out the form below or give us a call!</p>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                    <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                    <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n            <p style=\"margin-top: 20px;\"><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@harmonyhaven.com</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Harmony Haven Music School. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}